{"tid":654764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑獄 鄧龍威事件 香港人救香港人","createTime":"2018-05-06T02:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T02:43:07.000Z","uid":32991,"like":22,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"792b757278d5f4925511e5a0b670cdc6e598f9d5","tid":654764,"uid":32991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:15:19.000Z","msg":"今日咁啱睇完呢本書，覺得好恐怖。<br />\n本身我係冇留意到呢件事，直到今日。<br />\n用咗一日時間睇哂本書。<br />\n起菲律賓貪污問題太嚴重，竟然可以11年先有一個不公平既審訊，結果係被判終身監禁。<br />\n直到而家已經係18年既黑獄，我相信佢沒有犯毒。<br />\n因為能夠堅持18年都冇放棄既人一定有佢堅持的理由。<br />\n希望大家可以關注呢件事 <br />\n祝福佢可以早日回港<br />\n菲律賓真係一個好恐怖的地方，如果大家去呢個地方之前一定要特別小心謹慎。<br />\n含冤受屈的人內心一定好痛苦，普通人係唔能夠明白的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/06/101142_4d787ad05b318365ea19b3a2fc89663c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F06%2F101142_4d787ad05b318365ea19b3a2fc89663c.png&h=7f4b5273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/104929/菲獄風雲-捲毒案囚終身-鄧龍威獄中著書鳴冤-爆黑幕求翻案\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F104929%2F%E8%8F%B2%E7%8D%84%E9%A2%A8%E9%9B%B2-%E6%8D%B2%E6%AF%92%E6%A1%88%E5%9B%9A%E7%B5%82%E8%BA%AB-%E9%84%A7%E9%BE%8D%E5%A8%81%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%AD%E8%91%97%E6%9B%B8%E9%B3%B4%E5%86%A4-%E7%88%86%E9%BB%91%E5%B9%95%E6%B1%82%E7%BF%BB%E6%A1%88&d=65zmiEDbFJOKx0AN6DD1dDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=3a6e9c52\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/104929/菲獄風雲-捲毒案囚終身-鄧龍威獄中著書鳴冤-爆黑幕求翻案</a>"},{"pid":"1101a34be855f9d8e47ad73ec10ea7694f5ecc93","tid":654764,"uid":29314,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:16:37.000Z","msg":"「好人好姐做乜去傭人之國」？"},{"pid":"14da3977676fbd99a5129bf40e7171490eec16ab","tid":654764,"uid":32991,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1101a34be855f9d8e47ad73ec10ea7694f5ecc93","tid":654764,"uid":29314,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:16:37.000Z